Class TaskProperties

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      ca.ualberta.cs.c301_teamproject.TaskProperties

public class TaskProperties
extends Activity

This class is just used to gather the task properties. The properties are returned to CreateTask in a string array. The input is validated as well.
